    • addRefereeToMatch

      public void addRefereeToMatch(LocalDateTime date, String refereeName) throws IllegalArgumentException
      Takes in a Date/Time and the Name of the referee and tries to match the inputs up with their matching objects in the Tournament (the Match and the Referee, respectively). Also, checks to make sure the Referee isn't from a Country that has a Team Playing in that Match
      Parameters:
      date - the Start Date/Time of the match as a LocalDateTIme
      refereeName - as a String
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - when a Match at the given LocalDateTime doesn't exist, the Referee doesn't exist, or if the Referee is from a Country with a Team Playing in the Match
